#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/datetime_parser/_locales.jinja:1
msgid ""
"Given a list of strings sampled from a database column, identify the "
"datetime format."
msgstr "给定从数据库某一列中抽取的一组字符串，识别其日期时间格式。"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/datetime_parser/_locales.jinja:2
msgid ""
"If they are datetime strings of the same format, output the Python "
"strptime format string that can be used to parse them."
msgstr "如果它们是相同格式的日期时间字符串，输出可用于解析它们的 Python strptime 格式字符串。"

#: /Users/magolor/Utils/RubikSQL/RubikSQL-dev/src/rubiksql/resources/prompts/datetime_parser/_locales.jinja:3
msgid "If they are not datetime strings or have mixed formats, output None."
msgstr "如果它们不是日期时间字符串或格式混合，输出 None。"

